#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.162"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.162:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.162:0.2"
msgid "17. Paṭipadāvagga "
msgstr "17. Practice "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: dutiyapaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.162:0.3"
msgid "162. Vitthārasutta "
msgstr "162. In Detail "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.162:1.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, bhikkhave, paṭipadā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are four ways of practice. "

msgctxt "an4.162:1.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><ol>
msgctxt "an4.162:1.3"
msgid "Dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā. "
msgstr "~Painful practice with slow insight, ~painful practice with swift insight, ~pleasant practice with slow insight, and ~pleasant practice with swift insight. "

#. HTML: </ol><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.162:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā? "
msgstr "And what’s the painful practice with slow insight? "

msgctxt "an4.162:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pakatiyāpi tibbarāgajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ rāgajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr "It’s when someone is ordinarily full of acute greed, hate, and delusion. They often feel the pain and sadness that greed, hate, and delusion bring. "

msgctxt "an4.162:2.3"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi tibbadosajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ dosajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:2.4"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi tibbamohajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ mohajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:2.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni mudūni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "They have these five faculties weakly: "

msgctxt "an4.162:2.6"
msgid "saddhindriyaṃ, vīriyindriyaṃ, satindriyaṃ, samādhindriyaṃ, paññindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.162:2.7"
msgid "So imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ muduttā dandhaṃ ānantariyaṃ pāpuṇāti āsavānaṃ khayāya. "
msgstr "Because of this, they only slowly attain the conditions for ending the defilements in the present life. "

msgctxt "an4.162:2.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā. "
msgstr "This is called the painful practice with slow insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.150, sc3
msgctxt "an4.162:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā? "
msgstr "And what’s the painful practice with swift insight? "

msgctxt "an4.162:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pakatiyāpi tibbarāgajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ rāgajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr "It’s when someone is ordinarily full of acute greed, hate, and delusion. They often feel the pain and sadness that greed, hate, and delusion bring. "

msgctxt "an4.162:3.3"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi tibbadosajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ dosajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:3.4"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi tibbamohajātiko hoti, abhikkhaṇaṃ mohajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:3.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni adhimattāni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "And they have these five faculties strongly: "

msgctxt "an4.162:3.6"
msgid "saddhindriyaṃ, vīriyindriyaṃ, satindriyaṃ, samādhindriyaṃ, paññindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.162:3.7"
msgid "So imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ adhimattattā khippaṃ ānantariyaṃ pāpuṇāti āsavānaṃ khayāya. "
msgstr "Because of this, they swiftly attain the conditions for ending the defilements in the present life. "

msgctxt "an4.162:3.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā. "
msgstr "This is called the painful practice with swift insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.162:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sukhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā? "
msgstr "And what’s pleasant practice with slow insight? "

msgctxt "an4.162:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pakatiyāpi na tibbarāgajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ rāgajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr "It’s when someone is not ordinarily full of acute greed, hate, and delusion. They rarely feel the pain and sadness that greed, hate, and delusion bring. "

msgctxt "an4.162:4.3"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi na tibbadosajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ dosajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:4.4"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi na tibbamohajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ mohajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:4.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni mudūni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "They have these five faculties weakly: "

msgctxt "an4.162:4.6"
msgid "saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.162:4.7"
msgid "So imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ muduttā dandhaṃ ānantariyaṃ pāpuṇāti āsavānaṃ khayāya. "
msgstr "Because of this, they only slowly attain the conditions for ending the defilements in the present life. "

msgctxt "an4.162:4.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sukhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā. "
msgstr "This is called the pleasant practice with slow insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.162:5.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā? "
msgstr "And what’s the pleasant practice with swift insight? "

msgctxt "an4.162:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pakatiyāpi na tibbarāgajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ rāgajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr "It’s when someone is not ordinarily full of acute greed, hate, and delusion. They rarely feel the pain and sadness that greed, hate, and delusion bring. "

msgctxt "an4.162:5.3"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi na tibbadosajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ dosajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:5.4"
msgid "Pakatiyāpi na tibbamohajātiko hoti, nābhikkhaṇaṃ mohajaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.162:5.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni adhimattāni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "They have these five faculties strongly: "

msgctxt "an4.162:5.6"
msgid "saddhindriyaṃ, vīriyindriyaṃ, satindriyaṃ, samādhindriyaṃ, paññindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.162:5.7"
msgid "So imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ adhimattattā khippaṃ ānantariyaṃ pāpuṇāti āsavānaṃ khayāya. "
msgstr "Because of this, they swiftly attain the conditions for ending the defilements in the present life. "

msgctxt "an4.162:5.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā. "
msgstr "This is called the pleasant practice with swift insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.162:5.9"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, catasso paṭipadā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four ways of practice.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.162:5.10"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

